data.text:
Use the Search field to find publications in the Olympic World Library collection. When new publications are added they will be automatically included in the listings. The publications are either accessible in full text (digital files) or available for loan (including international loan) at The Olympic Studies Centre in Lausanne (studies.centre@olympic.org)

The Olympic World Library now also provides access to articles from the Journal of Olympic History (JOH) since its launch in 1992. Over 700 articles can be searched via this search engine.
